module REQ_PATIENT_Q_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-PATIENT-Q-01
 * Title       : Sort Patient Queue by Urgency and Arrival Time
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
